	; doc: @param station  string  the station partition
"RTN","VSLS3",90,0)
	; doc: @param ymd      string  YYYYMMDD day partition (default: today)
"RTN","VSLS3",91,0)
	; doc: @returns        string  the S3 object key
"RTN","VSLS3",92,0)
