"RTN","VSLTAPFC",69,0)
	; doc:                       byte-equal + hash-matched, with no missing and no extra
"RTN","VSLTAPFC",70,0)
	; doc: A drift (payload differs or hash stale) is a mismatch; a dropped record
"RTN","VSLTAPFC",71,0)
